extends layout.pug

block content

  article.portfolio-intro

    h1 My Programs

    p Check out what I've been up to the last few months. I had a lot of fun writing these projects. My personal favorite is the phrase guessing game.

  article.portfolio-project-thumbs
    .projects-box.box.grid
        each project in projects
          .cell
            a(href=`project/${project.id}`)
              img.thumbnail(src=`${project.image_urls.main}`, alt=`${project.description}`)
              h5= project.project_name

